MENU_PKG_BACULA
  Here you will find config options for the bacula backup application.

SDECFG_PKG_BACULE_DB
  Supported databases are: MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite3 or SQLite. Depending
  on the current package selection you should choose one of those. Leaving
  this as-is will result in a client-only package.
